going to fall under this machine learning branch. A third piece that's often used in

00:08:41.679 --> 00:08:47.119
that's often underestimated in terms of the value and significance for innovation is the

00:08:47.119 --> 00:08:52.080
combination of our domain knowledge with computer science skills that we term data stewardship,

00:08:52.960 --> 00:08:57.919
and it's at the intersection of all of these of where we find data science. Now, again, we didn't

