descriptors is key for packaging our projects into leverageable components that can further

00:10:52.320 --> 00:11:01.200
their overall innovative pipeline. To supplement this citizen data science program, we've defined

00:11:01.760 --> 00:11:07.840
a series of guidelines that we believe are critical towards the success here. Now, I'm not going to go

