that's encoded in that package so that it can continue to further innovation long past the

00:12:39.760 --> 00:12:45.119
lifetime of the individual project. We have a significant program named across all of these

00:12:46.080 --> 00:12:52.080
guidelines here. They're easier said than done, but this is our ambition for where we're aiming

00:12:52.080 --> 00:13:00.159
our citizen data science program to head towards. Of course, I'd be remiss if I didn't mention the

