like a 10-minute exercise where you don't have to go learn an entire ecosystem in order to start

00:13:58.960 --> 00:14:05.280
applying code-based data analysis to gain additional insights from your data. Third,

00:14:06.080 --> 00:14:12.239
we want to make sure that we have an extremely safe and secure environment that has robust data

00:14:12.239 --> 00:14:16.719
connectivity. So we're not spending much of our time trying to get access to the data. Instead,

